She would do best in a home without young children and with a dog friend as a companion.

pets.title: Tomlin.jpg
pets.description: Tomlin is a lovely medium-sized adult dog. He can be quite cheeky at the kennels, but Tomlin has been attending training classes here at HKDR and has already learnt Sit, Wait, Stay and Down. If you can give this loving dog a great home, please come down to Tai Po Homing Centre to meet him.
